{"tid":2340910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國產科興稱91%有效 何栢良：難作準","createTime":"2020-12-26T02:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T11:48:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f46ba00ae315f38fb906a89920accfec3f1940f","tid":2340910,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/CP27ETDAN5BOPIKKY253Q36MIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FCP27ETDAN5BOPIKKY253Q36MIY%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=0062c697\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FCP27ETDAN5BOPIKKY253Q36MIY%2F&h=ab779510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/CP27ETDAN5BOPIKKY253Q36MIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n國產科興稱91%有效 何栢良：難作準<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】獲特首林鄭月娥欽點的國產疫苗生產商中國科興，近月三度要求巴西當局延後公佈第三期中期臨床研究數據，另一參與試驗的國家土耳其終在當地時間星期四公開相關數據，惟僅涉及約1,300人的研究結果，佔總參與人數不足兩成。結果中有29人確診感染武漢肺炎，當中三人接種疫苗，並在感染後沒出現發燒等病徵，疫苗有效率約91%。有醫生認為，相關數據只屬初步，研究結果涉及人數少，暫未能就疫苗成效得出結論。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《蘋果》武肺疫苗問卷調查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/06-4rPuFZ80cxlP8LFUCqbgXboU=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YNHKMIXLC5C5VLD4J623J5GB6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F06-4rPuFZ80cxlP8LFUCqbgXboU%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYNHKMIXLC5C5VLD4J623J5GB6U.jpg&h=86ff4a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■土耳其早前向中國科興洽購疫苗作臨床試驗。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴西數據指50%至90%<br />\n<br />\n土耳其早前向中國科。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：袁國勇團隊：接種難阻無症狀傳染<br />\n<br />\n他指出，其他香港採購的疫苗如德國BioNtech的研究已有超過四萬人參與，但科興是次的數據未有年齡層、性別及病情等資料，結果也未經同行審核，加上涉及研究樣本數目少，不能就疫苗有效率作結論。呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超亦認為有關數據仍屬初步，涉及樣本人數少亦不能作準，須等待全面的數據才可得出準確的有效率。<br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問許樹昌則表示，土耳其的數據顯示疫苗初步成效理想，但因研究樣本數目少，仍要等待綜合巴西及印尼的第三期臨床研究結果，建議港府等待科興提供第三期臨床研究數據結果，及提供如疫苗成份等資料才再作審批。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局表示，採購協議下疫苗必須得到批准方可供應，而獲批准使用的疫苗必須通過臨床試驗，包括第三期研究數據。"},{"pid":"ad96d6427c557aabcc7ee0b1e714643aa76b9752","tid":2340910,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a480c435dbbce6ac0ddc489ce46c193bcbad426","tid":2340910,"uid":18477,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"何object已經犯咗党安法"},{"pid":"cb8e5f0f1ca80d6a0fb49bf66ed874b87f59fd2a","tid":2340910,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"多謝何醫生仲敢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eb88c9b64e8ebfd6c220967fb994c1b796f924","tid":2340910,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:15:50.000Z","msg":"專家打先，或者仲有少少少少少少說服力"},{"pid":"7c1ce8e2b7aaa385a6ff17fb271645bd15e27aa6","tid":2340910,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:32:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e006434b4a8129ecfcf6f0113fc1415d347ea9b","tid":2340910,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"大陸野吹水就叻如果真係咁好其實外國一早都買"},{"pid":"e06c07ceb0311fde12a4f56c0efea43ca6fdba0a","tid":2340910,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:19:57.000Z","msg":"阿7打先啦"},{"pid":"cc71bb34052c4c5be457b5444c069c2ae51e495f","tid":2340910,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB